data.description: Seller just reduced ready to negotiate Miller Home-This is a few blocks walk to the beach on beautiful Lake Michigan and the sand dunes with all its walking trails, surrounded by the Indiana Dunes Lakeshore West Beach and the Indiana Dunes National Lakeshore. This is an all brick 3 bedroom, one on the main level the other 2 bedrooms on the second floor. It has 2.5 bath,full bath main level and basement, second floor has a .25 bath. Beautiful, tranquil, setting surround by trees with nice size yard. There are hardwood floors, open concept kitchen/living, basement finished with a family room and bath. A nice concrete front open porch. You are less than 7 minutes from the South Shore connect to downtown Chicago and a few minutes to I65 and 80/94. Taxes do not reflect exemptions, so if you will be a homeowner with the Homestead deductions and other deductions, your taxes will decrease once you register with the county! Ready for you to move in. Must see to appreciate. Easy to show on a loc
